        <mxCell id="topo-box" value="&lt;b&gt;Topology Spread&lt;/b&gt;  maxSkew:1 per AZ + per Node&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pod Anti-Affinity&lt;/b&gt;  no two pods on same host"
